title: Demon Hunter Nearly Complete Collection - [AlphaGuardian]
description:
My nearly complete collection of Demon Hunter stuff as of January 2015. I'm missing True Defiance (Deluxe Edition). So if someone could hook me up with FLACs for that album I'd be grateful. These FLACs are uncompressed, ripped from CDs with DBpoweramp. Also includes uncompressed DVDs in .iso format ripped with DVDfab.

Support the artist! If you like the music, buy it.

Genre: Christian metal, metalcore, nu metal, groove metal, alternative metal

Included:
-Demon Hunter (2002)
-Summer of Darkness (2004)
-The Triptych (2005)
-Storm the Gates of Hell (Special Edition) (2007)
-45 Days Soundtrack (2008)
-45 Days Documentary DVD (2008)
-45 Days Live in Nashville DVD (2008)
-The World is a Thorn (Deluxe Edition) (2010)
-Extremist (Deluxe Edition) (2014)

Not Included:
"The Wind" single (2011)
True Defiance (2012)
